    "updated_at": "2016-06-30T21:38:31Z",
    "body": "Thanks for bringing this up, I've added support for customizing the location of the URL used to download ChromeDriver in https://github.com/electron/chromedriver/pull/3\n\nI've published new builds so if you use Spectron `3.2.4` or later, you should be able to set the `ELECTRON_MIRROR` environment variable to configure where it gets downloaded from and use a localhost URL or something else.\n\nPlease see https://github.com/electron/chromedriver#custom-mirror for more details.\n"
